title: List of storms named Kompasu
data: The name Kompasu has been used to name four tropical cyclones in the northwestern Pacific Ocean. The name was contributed by Japan and is the Japanese word for Compass (Circinus). In early 2023, the name Kompasu was announced to be retired and will no longer be used.[1] In spring 2024, It was replaced by Tokei, meaning Clock (Horologium).[2]
